CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

August 19, 2010

[Cite as 08/19/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-3860.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-1170. Arp v. Am. Family Ins. Co.

Lucas App. No. L-09-1110, 2010-0hio-2250. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
